<item>
            <title>[LU-11172] RPM build problem with GSSAPI</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11172</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;make rpms fails with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
RPM build errors:
    File not found: /tmp/rpmbuild-lustre-ashehata-0tAUfLMU/BUILDROOT/lustre-2.11.0_RC3_25_g7fe6043-1.x86_64/etc/init.d/lsvcgss
    File not found: /tmp/rpmbuild-lustre-ashehata-0tAUfLMU/BUILDROOT/lustre-2.11.0_RC3_25_g7fe6043-1.x86_64/etc/sysconfig/lsvcgss
    File not found: /tmp/rpmbuild-lustre-ashehata-0tAUfLMU/BUILDROOT/lustre-2.11.0_RC3_25_g7fe6043-1.x86_64/etc/request-key.d/lgssc.conf &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To resolve the following package needs to be installed:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
yum install keyutils-libs-devel &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The .spec file should make those files conditional based on whether GSSAPI was available for the build or not&lt;/p&gt;</description>
